name: Goldnet Sip Simple
author: Goldnet Australia

sections.description:
With this plugin, you can have a call centre or support desk on your website. You will be able to make or answer calls directly on your website.

Technical Details

This plugin will upgrade your website to a single point of contact by adding the voice call capability directly into it.
By activating this plugin your website will turn into a call center interface, without the need of any telephone devices or mobile apps.
Just setup your IP PBX for WEBRTC calls and get leverage of the best solution for call centre and website integration.
You can also use our cloud IP PBX or have our team set it up for you.
Please find more information at https://telcoservices.com.au/webphone
sections.installation:
This section describes how to install the plugin and get it working.

e.g.

  1. Upload the plugin files to the /wp-content/plugins/goldnet-sip-simple directory, or install the plugin through the WordPress plugins screen directly.
  2. Activate the plugin through the ‘Plugins’ screen in WordPress
